00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:30.710
Her extensive work as
an actor includes stage,

00:02:30.710 --> 00:02:32.460
film and television appearances,

00:02:32.460 --> 00:02:36.550 position:56%
and she has received four Lester
Horton awards for her reconstruction

00:02:36.550 --> 00:02:40.470
